# 1. Do you usually spend your days off with parents or friends?

It depends on the situation, but most of the time I spend my days off with friends because our schedules are quite similar as university students. We usually hang out, watch movies, play basketball or just have dinner together. However, when I go back to my hometown during holidays, I prefer spending time with my parents because I don’t get many chances to see them during the semester. I think both are important in different ways.

### 中文翻译：

这要看情况，不过大多数时候我会和朋友一起度过假期，因为作为大学生，我们的时间安排比较相似。我们通常会一起出去玩、看电影、打篮球，或者一起吃饭。不过，当我假期回老家的时候，我更喜欢陪父母，因为学期里其实没有太多机会见到他们。我觉得两者都很重要，只是意义不同。

---

# 2. What do you often do on your days off?

On my days off, I usually try to relax while still doing something meaningful. For example, I often sleep a little longer in the morning, then spend some time exercising or studying English, especially practicing IELTS speaking. In the evening, I might watch a science documentary or play games with friends online. I don’t like wasting the whole day doing nothing because I feel more satisfied when I balance rest and productivity.

### 中文翻译：

在休息日的时候，我通常会一边放松，一边做一些有意义的事情。比如，我会早上多睡一会儿，然后花点时间锻炼或者学习英语，尤其是练习雅思口语。到了晚上，我可能会看看科学纪录片，或者和朋友一起线上打游戏。我不太喜欢整天什么都不做，因为当休息和效率能够平衡的时候，我会更有满足感。

---

# 3. When was the last time you had a few days off?

The last time I had a few days off was during the recent public holiday. I stayed at home for several days and finally had the chance to slow down a bit after a busy period of studying. During that break, I reorganized my study plans, caught up on sleep and spent more time with my family. Although it wasn’t a long vacation, it really helped me recharge mentally.

### 中文翻译：

我上一次有几天假期是在最近的法定节假日。我在家待了几天，在经历了一段忙碌的学习之后，终于有机会让自己慢下来。在那个假期里，我重新整理了学习计划、补了觉，还花了更多时间陪家人。虽然假期不算长，但它确实让我在精神上恢复了很多。

---

# 4. What would you like to do if you had a day off tomorrow?

If I had a day off tomorrow, I’d probably arrange a very relaxing but productive day. In the morning, I’d like to go to a café with my laptop and work on some AI-related projects or personal ideas. Then in the afternoon, I’d probably go for a walk in a park or play some sports to clear my mind. At night, I’d watch a movie or read something interesting before going to bed early. That sounds like an ideal day to me.

### 中文翻译：

如果我明天放假的话，我可能会安排一个既放松又高效的一天。早上我想带着电脑去咖啡馆，做一些 AI 相关项目或者自己的想法。下午的话，我可能会去公园散步，或者运动一下，让大脑放松。到了晚上，我会看看电影或者读点有意思的东西，然后早点睡觉。对我来说，这就是非常理想的一天。
